PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#>
PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>
PREFIX yago: <http://yago-knowledge.org/resource/>
PREFIX y2geor: <http://kr.di.uoa.gr/yago2geo/resource/>
PREFIX y2geoo: <http://kr.di.uoa.gr/yago2geo/ontology/>
SELECT DISTINCT ?stream ?type WHERE {
  <http://yago-knowledge.org/resource/Lake_Michigan> geo:hasGeometry ?lakeGeo .
  
  ?stream rdf:type <http://kr.di.uoa.gr/yago2geo/ontology/OSM_stream> .
  ?stream geo:hasGeometry ?streamGeo .
  ?stream <http://kr.di.uoa.gr/yago2geo/ontology/hasSource> ?source .
  ?stream <http://kr.di.uoa.gr/yago2geo/ontology/hasMouth> ?mouth .
  ?source geo:hasGeometry ?sourceGeo .
  ?mouth geo:hasGeometry ?mouthGeo .
  
  FILTER(geof:sfIntersects(?streamGeo, ?lakeGeo)) .
  
  {
    FILTER(geof:sfWithin(?mouthGeo, ?lakeGeo)) .
    BIND("inflow" AS ?type)
  }
  UNION
  {
    FILTER(geof:sfWithin(?sourceGeo, ?lakeGeo)) .
    BIND("outflow" AS ?type)
  }
}

PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#>
PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>
PREFIX yago: <http://yago-knowledge.org/resource/>
PREFIX y2geor: <http://kr.di.uoa.gr/yago2geo/resource/>
PREFIX y2geoo: <http://kr.di.uoa.gr/yago2geo/ontology/>
SELECT DISTINCT ?borderingCounty WHERE {
  <http://yago-knowledge.org/resource/County_Donegal> geo:hasGeometry ?donegalGeo .
  ?donegalGeo geo:asWKT ?donegalWKT .
  
  ?borderingCounty a ?countyClass .
  FILTER(?countyClass IN (<http://kr.di.uoa.gr/yago2geo/ontology/OSI_County_Council>, <http://kr.di.uoa.gr/yago2geo/ontology/OSI_City_and_County_Council>))
  
  ?borderingCounty geo:hasGeometry ?borderingGeo .
  ?borderingGeo geo:asWKT ?borderingWKT .
  
  FILTER(geof:sfTouches(?borderingWKT, ?donegalWKT))
  
  FILTER(?borderingCounty != <http://yago-knowledge.org/resource/County_Donegal>)
}

question: Which districts border Warwickshire?
gold_query:

PREFIX strdf: <http://strdf.di.uoa.gr/ontology#>

PREFIX y2geor: <http://kr.di.uoa.gr/yago2geo/resource/>

SELECT DISTINCT ?district WHERE { yago:Warwickshire geo:hasGeometry ?o1 . ?o1 geo:asWKT ?geoWKT1 . ?district rdf:type y2geoo:OS_District ; geo:hasGeometry ?o2 . ?o2 geo:asWKT ?geoWKT2 FILTER geof:sfTouches(?geoWKT1, ?geoWKT2) }
